=============== CONFIG_GPIO_SYSFS ===============
Due to linux kernel 5.5 above deprecated GPIO_SYSFS, so need to enable by menuconfig

bitbake linux-imx -c menuconfig
1. enable embadded_system
2. enable device driver > gpio support > GPIO SYSFS


