3. make && sudo make install
4. after finished the compile, cd to bin diretory
   cd bin
5. Exec libwebsocket-test-server   
   ./libwebsockets-test-server
6. Open a browser
   chromium --no-sandbox
7. type localhost:7681/
finished libwebsockets test.


